##<a id='install'></a> Install and Configure Instana Microservices Application Monitoring

To install the Instana Microservices Application Monitoring file on the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard, do the following:

1. Download the product file from Pivotal Network.

1. Navigate to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Import a Product** to upload the product file. 

1. Under the **Import a Product** button, click **+** next to the version number of Instana Microservices Application Monitoring. 
This adds the tile to your staging area.

1. Click the newly added **Instana Microservices Application Monitoring** tile.

